name: Tokyo Night
lyrics:
作词 : Lunak/Victorm
作曲 : Lunak/Victorm
编曲 : Lunak/Victorm
There's nothing you do, I don't see
你什么都不做，我不明白
This isn't my first time, but in a while
这不是我第一次，但过了一会
Oh, playing with fire
引火上身
Cause your kiss is sweet, but it's killing me
因为你的吻很甜蜜，但快要让我窒息
You shouldn't ever pick from the poison
你永远不应该选择毒药
Trained, I know your tricks
故意的，我知道你的把戏
Still I fall for it
我还是喜欢它
Like I never will
就像我永远不会
Guess I like to get fired
看来我喜欢被解雇
收起
